questionvariables.text:
v1: rand_with_step(1,9,1);
v2: rand_with_step(2,9,1); 
v3: rand_with_step(1,9,1); 
gl: |x+v1|=v2*x-v3
l1: (v1+v3)/(v2-1);
l2: (v3-v1)/(v2+1);
loesung: if(l1>=-v1) and (l2<-v1) then {l1,l2} else if(l1>=-v1) and (l2>-v1) then {l1} else if(l1<-v1) and (l2<-v1) then {l2} else {};
